{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"98337-sports-day","title":"Sports Day","description":"Lace up your shoes, drink some water, and get ready for Sports Day. Happy, sad, nervous, excited - the students of KV School are feeling so many emotions. Aska-lakadi-gala-galoo, cheer them, won’t you?","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Menaka Raman"],"illustrators":["Jemma Jose"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/98337-sports-day"},"cover":{"card":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/495676/size3/969538e582d44ed3863f7c2fe495445a.jpg","large":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/495676/size6/969538e582d44ed3863f7c2fe495445a.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/144415/size6/e528b93d258bae1e39604a487b426985.jpg","text":"Today is Sports Day at KV School.\nWho will win? Who will lose?","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/142816/size6/0f6b40e275f58028a6d92bdbfd50debc.jpg","text":"Marching proudly to the beat\nLeft, right, left go Koki’s feet!","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/142817/size6/71dce90e107230f6fff14257516f2c78.jpg","text":"Mass drill, right before the races,\nLook at all those happy faces!","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/142818/size6/dd6838823f2d29af0eeb920ded78a14d.jpg","text":"Ewwww, squeals Jojo,\nCHEE, CHEE, CHEE,\nSuch sweaty armpits in kabbadi!","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/142821/size6/97a79ce896d83847c4d88159184fe9d0.jpg","text":"ASKA-LAKADI-GALA-GALOO,\nThe houses are cheering,\nit’s hullabaloo!","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/142822/size6/b01d690bb5c21c9d90226b4ae8b294e0.jpg","text":"The runners line up for relay\nWill Rani finally beat BJ?","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/142823/size6/e476d3b15c4052d299ff8841eabb26a7.jpg","text":"Manju’s sad she cannot run,\nBut didn’t want to miss the fun.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/142824/size6/d7df7fbcfc1d31315a61643ca7cbbfcf.jpg","text":"Vasu’s tummy goes round and round.\nHe’s scared to let his team down.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/142825/size6/53e8ad9169f9f461e784b86264fe0cb9.jpg","text":"On your marks, get set, go!\nThe runners are off, toe-to-toe!\nBJ’s angry, her face is red.\nRani’s team is way ahead","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/142826/size6/2afd155627025d96bd6e360ffc4bec8e.jpg","text":"The cheering crowds can’t believe it.\nRani’s team’s won by a minute!","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/142843/size6/b5e3f7f552e39a354e87e26865b3d52b.jpg","text":"Shiny medals and big cups\nThe winners proudly hold them up.\nThe others wipe away their tears\nAnd promise to try again next year!","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/143474/size6/f4157d5aef7205025e1aa87ca7834286.jpg","text":"13/13","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":12,"words":149}}